name: DonkrDeLafuma
description:
It's my cat. His name is Donkr. Today he is 10 years old ! I made sketch of this artwork when he was 6 years old. 
Today is his special day so I decided to put some colors from the base sketch and put it in here.

I always see and portray him as a puma or black phanter, because he look that way haha.
Always being a good boi all these years. Even my friend said he is so creepy, because he always stare at me from the gate of my house.

I want to treat him a wagyu beef haha, so I made this NFT artwork :)

Cheers!
